data.text:
Post by michael7627 on

1st Single/Buzz Track (You know how it goes) from Trina's 5th album Amazin'

The track is a great uptempo rap track. Trina once again proclaims she's the queen and is not sorry for being conceited because "That's My Attitude"!

Really hoping this makes some noise because Trina has gotten progressively better with each album and Still Da Baddest was one of my favorite rap CDs of 2008 as well as her best album.

Collaborations confirmed for Amazin' include: Drew Sidora, Jagged Edge, Keri Hilson, Lady Gaga, Ludacris, Lyfe Jennings, Nicki Minaj, Pretty Money, Rick Ross, Shonie, and Swazy Baby.

Album in stores 9/22/09 but expect it to chance since she just officially released the first single 9/4/09

Post by C.Ro on

I definitely hope she make some noise..here we go was amazing..and that lady gaga colab sounds interesting!
